"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/54/14183/abstract/3\">",
"      Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC). Adverse health conditions and health risk behaviors associated with intimate partner violence--United States, 2005. MMWR Morb Mortal Wkly Rep 2008; 57:113.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     The World Health Organization. World report on violence and health. Chapter 4. Violence by intimate partners. file://www.who.int/violence_injury_prevention/violence/global_campaign/en/chap4.pdf (Accessed on August 07, 2011).",
